Repeat: yo, sl 1 wyib, drop the yo of the preceding row off the needle, k3
yo, sl both the yo and slip stitch of the preceding row, p3
yo, slip the 2 yo's and slip stitch of the preceding rows, k3
yo, sl the 3 yo's amd slip stitch of the preceding rows, p3

insert right hand needle from behind under the bundle of 4 yo strands (but not the slip stitch) and purl these strands together, then knit the slip stitch; then insert the left needle from the front under the 4 yo strands and purl them together again; k3
